						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in the Nārāyaṇadēva temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 12th Century.</p>						

						<p>This seems to record a gift of land to the god Gōpāla by Basavarasa and the <hi rend="italic">Prabhus</hi> of Sāḷavāḍige. The inscription is damaged.</p>						

